Package emfmodeldistance

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IEReferenceNavigator
    This interface provides functionality to navigate through the references of an EObject in an Ecore model.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DistanceCalculator
    This is the class that MOMot uses to calculate the distance between two models.
    DistanceUtil
    This class defines the interface of the utility functions to compute the distance between two ECore models.
    EcoreShortestPaths
    This class allows to compute the shortests number of links from an EObject to another, given an ordered list of EObject from an Ecore model.
    MoveDistance
    This class calculates the move distance between two models.
